<h1>Connections</h1>
<p class='pub-date mb-4'>Published: Thursday, December 21, 2023 at 4:00 pm -0800</p>
<img src='/images/gaming/connections/connections-title.png' alt='' class='img-fluid pb-3'>	
<p class='intro'>
	Another fun game in the NYT games subscription, <i>Connections</i> is one of my favorite games from 2023. 
</p>
<p>Connections is an entertaining word game that challenges you to discover four sets of words in a grid connected by a common theme. While some groups may be straightforward, like colors or states, the real excitement arises when words with multiple meanings are involved, potentially fitting into various categories.</p>
<p>For instance, consider the word SPICE, which may seem associated with PEPPER and SALT on the board, yet it could be a clever distraction meant to mislead you. In reality, it might belong to a group of words concluding with &quot;GIRLS,&quot; linking SPICE with INDIGO.</p>
<p>These puzzles are easily accessible on your phone, providing a delightful and engaging experience.</p>
<h3>Some Puzzles I've Created</h3>
<p>I discovered an online puzzle generator that enables the creation of custom puzzles, and I've been thoroughly enjoying the process of crafting them!</p>
